Recommends: raspi-config
Description: PAMGuard passive acoustic monitoring for Raspberry Pi Zero
 WhalePi turns a Raspberry Pi Zero 2 W and a COSMOS DAQ card into a flexible
 passive acoustic recording and real-time analysis system based on PAMGuard.
 .
 This package installs all prerequisites (Java 21, SQLite, Bluetooth LE
 support, tmux, etc.), downloads and unpacks the PAMGuard firmware, and
 configures the Pi (I2C, microphone, Bluetooth) ready to run the watchdog.
